-- Bahrain to Probe Fire at Isa Town Market, State-Agency Says
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h
-- 2012-07-16T03:28:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-16/bahrain-to-probe-fire-at-isa-town-market-state-agency-says.html
Bahrain will start today an
investigation to find out the reasons behind a fire at a
traditional market in Bahrain’s Isa town, the state-run Bahrain
News Agency reported, citing General Tariq al-Hassan, the chief
of public security.  Firefighters have battled and controlled the fire that
erupted yesterday, the BNA said, citing officials it didn’t
identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
